div.p: I wouldn’t say it was enjoyable I would say it was... I don’t look back on it through the rose coloured specs of people saying
those were the best times of your life, no, I look back and I did alright, I did well but I didn’t ever fit in in any specific group
so I was a chameleon, I could flit from the sporty types to the academic types to the bad boys but never ever fitting in in one particular group of those
so there was a little bit of outsider as well.
